{"tid":52850,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★傳iOS10.2讓非iPhone6s機型出現電池問題!!!!!!!","createTime":"2016-12-24T10:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T12:20:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30c13b5e9c79a5b2398083f8d2ccbc46722d64f8","tid":52850,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tech.hk.dailyeconomic.com/2016/12/24/5681.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftech.hk.dailyeconomic.com%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F5681.html&d=ORkV3TibX6eVz69FFHa7AEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c78f5f94\" target=\"_blank\">http://tech.hk.dailyeconomic.com/2016/12/24/5681.html</a><br />\n<br />\n非 iPhone 6s 機型在升級到 iOS 10.2 系統之後，電量會在降低到某一個百分比之後定格，繼續使用設備也不會降低電量。而如果繼續使用的話，設備就會出現隨機的百分比掉電。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92371674f2b1d416dfaeaf99c068618bcff11e43","tid":52850,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131285a6c94cae6ef0d9baa8b188e741dc650293","tid":52850,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:38:10.000Z","msg":"在蘋果官方支持的社區論壇上，一個關於 iPhone 6s 以外的機型出現電池問題的帖子的回復已經<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">超過了 62 頁</span>，不少用戶都抱怨稱，這個問題是在升級 iOS 10.2 之後才出現的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c396a4ab5f8f312